quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,28,"Niwaba hakana mugabo urondera imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe wizera, rero nuvugane nabo amajambo yoroshe"
  17,29,"Kandi ntugire ukuboko kwawe nkukwabohewe mw’izosi ryawe, canke ntukuzingurure nabi nabi bazoca baguterako umwikomo nukurwa mubukene"
  17,30,"Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azingururira imigisha yayo kuwo yishakiye, nukuyima uwo yishakiye mu vy’ukuri nayo kubashumvyi bayo niyo ibazi nukuba bona"
  17,31,"Kandi ntimuhekure ibibondo vyanyu mugutinya ubukene, ni twebwe tubaha imigisha yacu hamwe namwe, mu vy’ukuri ukubica n’igicumuro kininiya cane"
  17,32,"Kandi ntimwegere ubushurashuzi mu vy’ukuri ubwo bushurashuzi n’umwanda muniniya cane, kandi n’inzira mbi cane"
  17,33,"Kandi ntimwice umutima waho Imana yabujije kuwica atari munzira y’ukuri, n’uwiciwe munzira z’ubuhemu tuzomuha inguvu uwuzo sigarira, kandi mu vy’ukuri azofashwa"
  17,34,"Kandi ntimwegere amatungo y’Impfuvyi atari munzira nziza kugeza aho izo mpfuvyi zizoba zageze mubigero vy’ugukura, kandi mwitegereze amasezerano yanyu mu vy’ukuri amasezerano azobazwa k’umusi w’imperuka"
  17,35,"Kandi nimukwize ibipimo mupimirako, kandi mupime kuminzani ikwiye, ivyo navyo nivyo vyiza kuri mwebwe kandi bikaba ari vyiza mumpera ya vyose"
  17,36,"Kandi ntukurikire uwudafise ubumenyi mu vy’ukuri amatwi hamwe n’amaso n’umutima, ivyo vyose bizobazwa"
  17,37,"Kandi ntugire kuri iy’Isi wishima, mu vy’ukuri wewe ntushobora gusatura iy’Isi, canke ngo ushikire k’uburebure bw’Imisozi yayo"
  17,38,Ibi vyose ububi bwavyo nubwo gushavuza imbere y’Umuremyi wawe